<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idab534e0a-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s8901"><num value="8901">§ 8901.</num><heading> Composition</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Naval Militia consists of the Naval Militia of the States, the District of Columbia, Guam, and the Virgin Islands.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idab534e0b-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5">(<ref href="/us/act/1956-08-10/ch1041">Aug. 10, 1956, ch. 1041</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/70A/486">70A Stat. 486</ref>, § 7851; <ref href="/us/pl/109/163/dA/tX/s1057/a/11">Pub. L. 109–163, div. A, title X, § 1057(a)(11)</ref>, <date date="2006-01-06">Jan. 6, 2006</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/119/3441">119 Stat. 3441</ref>; renumbered § 8901, <ref href="/us/pl/115/232/dA/tVIII/s807/d/11">Pub. L. 115–232, div. A, title VIII, § 807(d)(11)</ref>, <date date="2018-08-13">Aug. 13, 2018</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/132/1837">132 Stat. 1837</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
